    You see the shimmer of a tear, but she wipes it away before it can earn an identity.

    <<speech "allura">>It wasn't until years later, in Altherin, that I met a Seer who told me more about my patronage. She did a ritual with a drop of my blood... and found a name buried deep inside it.<</speech>>

    <<speech "allura">><em>Traloin.</em><</speech>>

    <<speech "jaylie">>Is that a name I should know?<</speech>>

    <<speech "allura">>If you studied the Jade Coast wars, you might. He wasn't just a demon. He was responsible for razing half of Medmarr and almost destroying Hale about two centuries ago.<<speech>>

